Intelligent Systems Corp's AsherTechnologies Inc said it introduced two facsimile products, aportable unit and an internal card for IBM personal computersand compatibles.    The JT facsimile products are designed for use with the IBMPC, XT, AT, or compatibles to send or receive group IIItransmissioins, the company said.    Asher said the new products eliminate printing out hardcopies and manually sending each sheet to be transmitted.    The internal unit retails for 395 dlrs, while the portableunit sells for 495 dlrs, the company said. Reuter&#3;